        {
            "title": "港元隔夜拆息抽升至2.77厘 創逾一個半月新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港元拆息在今日月結及季結之下抽升，港元隔夜拆息漲逾47點子，升至2.77厘，扭轉上日跌勢，創逾一個半月新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其餘期限拆息則延續跌勢，1個月及3個月拆息均創近一星期新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">樓按相關的1個月拆息報2.235厘，跌約5點子。反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息報約2.357厘，跌5.5點子。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817037-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e9%9a%94%e5%a4%9c%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e6%8a%bd%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b32-77%e5%8e%98-%e5%89%b5%e9%80%be%e4%b8%80%e5%80%8b%e5%8d%8a%e6%9c%88%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 12:01:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股半日跌  深股挫近1.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日挫，深股及創業板表現差，深股跌近1.5%，創板跌逾2.3%，兩市成交合計13307.54億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日報3908，跌15點或0.38%，今早以3924點開市，升不足1點或0.02%，早段高見3948點，升25點或0.64%，中段反覆向下，低見3904，跌19點或0.48%，半日成交5916.2億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日報13526，跌199點或1.45%，今早開市報13683點，則跌42點或0.31%。中段見13783，升57點或0.42%，為上午高位，即拾級而下，臨近收市低見13503，挫223點或1.62%，半日成交7391.34億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日跌25點0.58%，報4465點，今早開跌不足1點，開報4491點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日跌77點或2.36%，報3196點，今早開市報3247點，跌26點或0.8%。</p>\n</div>",
